short_description: A documentary that takes you inside the Collingwood Football Club during the 2023 AFL Finals series, following its coach and three of its star players, as they attempt to lead their team to its sixteenth premiership.
facts_and_links: {'Goofs': ["The three-quarter-time Grand Final score displayed on screen during the match footage montage is incorrect. Brisbane's score is listed as 9.3 (57), indicating a Collingwood lead of 18 points. This was, in fact, Brisbane's half-time score. Brisbane's correct three-quarter-time score was 11.5 (71), giving Collingwood a lead of 4 points.", 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt31417201/goofs/?tab=gf&ref_=tt_dyk_gf'], 'Connections': ['Featured in Friday Night Football: Round 1: Collingwood vs Sydney (2024)', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt31417201/movieconnections/?ref_=tt_dyk_cnn']}
